overview: One of the things CF is most famous for is introducing guys to the joys of pleasing another man. This fifth installment of First Time Fucks keeps that proud tradition going. Seeing a guy's eyes light up when he experiences that electric thrill is always a hot moment, and these four scenes where our veterans break in Avery, Clint, Cooper, and Max are sure to excite you.
title: First Time Fucks 5
